Russia Seeks End of ‘Indiscriminate’ Libya Attacks

-- B y   S t e p h e n   B i e r m a n
-- 
2011-03-20T13:41:39Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-20/russia-seeks-end-of-indiscriminate-libya-attacks.html
Russia’s Foreign Affairs Ministry
asked that coalition forces, including those from the  United
States ,  France  and the U.K., stop non-selective attacks in  Libya , the ministry said in a statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Stephen Bierman in Moscow 
